          include ../includes/_affiliate-disclaimer.pug
          p
            | Growing up, Risk was always one of #[em the] board games, alongside Sorry, Monopoly, and Scrabble. It‚Äôs satisfying to plan a grand strategy and win territory in Risk, but each game takes so long to play (and often is never finished at all)!
