            br
            | These modern games build on many of Risk‚Äôs mechanics but deliver a more balanced and engaging experience with a shorter play time.
        .section(id=`${toID(rec1)}`)
          h2 #{rec1}
          img(src='../img/root-close-up.jpg' alt='Root board game close up')
          .caption
              | Photo credit:&nbsp;
              a.text-link(href="https://boardgamegeek.com/image/4285889/root") @Romn, on BGG
          .tags
            .tag
              .icon
                img(src='../img/puzzle.svg' alt='complexity')
              | More Complex
            .tag
              .icon
                img(src='../img/people.svg' alt='player count')
              | 2-4 Players
            .tag
              .icon
                img(src='../img/time.svg' alt='play time')
